{
  "doc_id": "3906",
  "text": "Firstly, in comparison to previous reports of limitedevidence 41, 43 showing no-difference between true and sham manipulation, the results of this SR show moderate to strong evidence [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] for the beneficial effects of MT1 in comparison to sham-MT1. These differences are demonstrated in terms of pain relief, functional improvement, and overall-health and quality of life improvements in the short-term for all stages of LBP.",
